  "title": "Facilities Management Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of performing daily operational activities in commercial building which includes attending to tenants' enquiries, needs and complaints.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in performing preventive and breakdown technical support and maintenance for<strong> </strong>mechanical/electrical services, plumbing &amp; sanitary services, Aircon servicing and maintenance, ACMV systems, chillers, and electrical control</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Nitec in Mechanical / Electrical Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>Min 2 years of working experience in facilities management/ ACMV</li>\n  <li>Rotating shift is requried</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
